author: STEPHEN COHEN, SEATTLEPI.COM
title: Watch: 'Bad man' Russell Wilson stars in new commercial with Macklemore
text:
Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson appeared alongside one of Seattle's brightest musical stars in a new ad for Bose wireless headphones.
In the ad, Wilson is seen lounging around his palatial home -- who knows if it's the $6.7 million Bellevue mansion he reportedly purchased in September. Grammy-winning rapper Macklemore is also there, pumping up the Super Bowl-winning quarterback with some unusual encouragement, like "Who's that bad man making a smoothie?"
